  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

  Function :   This Edit macro allows all the JCL DD statements to be
  ----------   reformatted with one parameter by line.

  Operation :  starting at the top of the data, all DD statements are
  -----------  reformatted by beeing copied one parameter at a time
               (new lines are inserted into the data to contain all
               the reformatted DD statements). Anything other than
               part of a DD statement is left as is.

  Command syntax : FLOWJCL
  ---------------- FLOWJCL HELP or H
